{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0681b86ca6","title":"对参加保卫延安的人民解放军部分领导干部的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"24d2505c05","index":0,"year":1947,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"0681b86ca6"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"327f6da09b","type":"paragraph","text":"对参加保卫延安的人民解放军部分","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"0681b86ca6"},{"id":"b9a41979ed","type":"paragraph","text":"领导干部的讲话口","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"0681b86ca6"},{"id":"aee0daa90a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年3月18日）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"0681b86ca6"},{"id":"410d01b8eb","type":"paragraph","text":"教人要来了，我们准备给他打扫房子。我军打仗，不在一城一地的得失，而在于消灭敌人的有生力量。存人失地，人地皆存：存地失人，人地皆失。敌人进延安是握着拳头的，他到了延安，就要把指头伸开，这样就便于我们一个一个地切掉它。要告诉同志们：少则一年，多则二年，我们就要回来，我们要以一个延安换取全中国。[1]这是毛泽东在撤离延安之前，接见参加保卫延安的人民解放军部分领导干部时讲话的一部分。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"0681b86ca6"}],"page":{"id":"a460f73ff9","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"0681b86ca6","start":465,"end":465}}}},"__N_SSG":true}